tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE historical_claims (
    claim_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    member_id INT,
    claim_date DATE,
    diagnosis_code VARCHAR(10),
    procedure_code VARCHAR(10),
    billed_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
    paid_amount DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE Claims (
	claim_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	member_id INT,
	diagnosis_code VARCHAR(10),
	claim_amount DECIMAL(10,2),
	service_date DATE
);
